
This directory contains sub-directories:

  examples/

    Sources of example programs demonstrating the synchronisation
    primatives defined in libsrc/ directory.

  libsrc/

    Sources for the extra synchronisation primitives (BARRIER,
    BUCKET, CREW and SEMAPHORE).

Note: documentation for BARRIER, BUCKET and SEMAPHORE can be found
in ../docs/hlps.txt.  See examples/crew_test.occ for illustration of
what the CREW primitive does and how it should be used. 


Peter Welch
